<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 18:08:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>拜登在以色列与哈马斯战争中的新常态：亲巴勒斯坦质问者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bidens-new-normal-amid-the-israel-hamas-war-pro-palestinian-hecklers/0000018d-5b38-d6b0-adcd-7fba045d0000</link><description>随着拜登连任竞选活动进入新阶段，他对以色列加沙战争的支持促使有组织的亲巴勒斯坦抗议者团体在弗吉尼亚州、南卡罗来纳州、伊利诺伊州、华盛顿州、明尼苏达州和战场州密歇根州采取行动。总统正在流失民主党的支持</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 17:53:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/bidens-new-normal-amid-the-israel-hamas-war-pro-palestinian-hecklers/0000018d-5b38-d6b0-adcd-7fba045d0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡誓言以色列军队不会离开加沙，数千名恐怖分子不会作为人质协议的一部分被释放</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-will-not-exit-gaza-thousands-of-terrorists-will-not-be-freed-in-deal/0000018d-5ade-d997-adff-dffe928f0000</link><description>以色列反对派领导人亚伊尔·拉皮德表示，该党将为内塔尼亚胡政府提供“安全网”，以达成协议释放人质，但该党消息人士称，该提议的细节仍不清楚</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 15:52:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-idf-will-not-exit-gaza-thousands-of-terrorists-will-not-be-freed-in-deal/0000018d-5ade-d997-adff-dffe928f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府新闻办公室接待呼吁轰炸伊朗的福音派领袖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-press-office-hosts-evangelical-leader-who-calls-for-bombing-iran/0000018d-5a7e-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fd6440000</link><description>在一场题为“10 月 7 日战争中的以色列和外国媒体”的活动中，基督教领袖迈克·埃文斯 (Mike Evans) 表示，美国应该攻击哈格岛，因为“伊朗 90% 的原油都存放在那里”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-press-office-hosts-evangelical-leader-who-calls-for-bombing-iran/0000018d-5a7e-d0fc-a9bd-5e7fd6440000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯领导人表示，该组织收到了在巴黎提出的加沙战争停火建议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/hamas-chief-says-group-received-gaza-war-cease-fire-proposal-put-forward-in-paris/0000018d-5a24-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d9daf0000</link><description>据称，该协议的第一阶段包括释放约 35 名以色列人质，以换取六周的战斗中断，以及从以色列监狱释放数千名巴勒斯坦囚犯</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:49:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/hamas-chief-says-group-received-gaza-war-cease-fire-proposal-put-forward-in-paris/0000018d-5a24-d0fc-a9bd-5e7d9daf0000</guid></item><item><title>“必须击败这些怪物”：内塔尼亚胡称加沙战争也为西方而战，回避了10月7日的指责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/must-defeat-these-monsters-netanyahu-says-gaza-war-also-battle-for-west-evades-blame/0000018d-5a5f-d997-adff-df7f80000000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在与新保守派作家道格拉斯·默里的谈话中强调，以色列需要在加沙地带“全面战胜”哈马斯，他说“如果野蛮主义在这里获胜，欧洲将是下一个”。美国将是下一个”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 14:27:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/must-defeat-these-monsters-netanyahu-says-gaza-war-also-battle-for-west-evades-blame/0000018d-5a5f-d997-adff-df7f80000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列正走向极右翼与人质家属之间的巷战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-heading-towards-street-battles-between-the-far-right-and-families-of-hostages/0000018d-59c6-d997-adff-ddfe963b0000</link><description>极右翼部长斯莫特里奇和本格维尔有一个共同的目标：将中间派甘茨赶出战时内阁并要求获得席位。现在，一切似乎都朝着对他们有利的方向发展</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:23:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-is-heading-towards-street-battles-between-the-far-right-and-families-of-hostages/0000018d-59c6-d997-adff-ddfe963b0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙反乌托邦帐篷城市的生活：“我感觉我失去了一切”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mud-world-gazans-build-a-new-society-in-dystopian-tent-cities/0000018d-5a59-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d50890000</link><description>加沙南部已成为一个巨大的帐篷营地：Fidaa al-Qurshali 博士设立了一个免费诊所，而“塔里克老师”则将他的帐篷变成了教室。尽管严重拥挤和短缺，拉法流离失所的巴勒斯坦人仍勉强度日</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 13:14:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/mud-world-gazans-build-a-new-society-in-dystopian-tent-cities/0000018d-5a59-d0fc-a9bd-5e5d50890000</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯摇滚乐队 Bi-2 的以色列成员正在前往以色列的途中，而其他成员在俄罗斯的压力下仍被泰国拘留</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/under-russian-pressure-rock-band-bi-2-will-remain-in-arrest-in-thailand/0000018d-5a3f-d6b0-adcd-7ebfb2d40001</link><description>乐队成员担心俄罗斯是他们被捕的幕后黑手，因为他们公开反对乌克兰战争，他们拒绝会见参观他们拘留中心的俄罗斯驻泰国领事，他们的释放被取消</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:39:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/under-russian-pressure-rock-band-bi-2-will-remain-in-arrest-in-thailand/0000018d-5a3f-d6b0-adcd-7ebfb2d40001</guid></item><item><title>他们逃离普京的战争来到以色列。然后不得不第二次逃离</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/refugees-again-war-drove-them-out-of-ukraine-then-from-their-homes-in-israel/0000018d-598f-d6b0-adcd-7dbfdf120000</link><description>他们希望在以色列找到一个安全的避难所——结果却不得不再次逃离：“我们意识到无处可返回”</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:27:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/refugees-again-war-drove-them-out-of-ukraine-then-from-their-homes-in-israel/0000018d-598f-d6b0-adcd-7dbfdf120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军解雇涉嫌谋杀巴勒斯坦人的以色列定居者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-suspected-of-murdering-palestinians-released-from-idf-service/0000018d-5a07-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f34850000</link><description>Shin Bet 安全部门要求解除 Chaim Pearlman 的预备役职务，他仍然是 1998 年耶路撒冷一系列未侦破的刺伤事件的主要嫌疑人。以色列国防军表示，皮尔曼入伍时并不知道此事</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 12:13:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-settler-suspected-of-murdering-palestinians-released-from-idf-service/0000018d-5a07-d0fc-a9bd-5e5f34850000</guid></item><item><title>近东救济工程处是什么？它服务的巴勒斯坦难民是谁？为什么各国冻结资金？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-unrwa-and-why-are-countries-freezing-their-funding/0000018d-550e-d0fc-a9bd-5f5f45020000</link><description>该联合国机构提供教育、卫生和社会服务，并在战争时期提供救生援助和庇护所，目前是加沙最大的雇主之一。但有关哈马斯参与的指控可能会危及其行动</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:32:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/what-is-unrwa-and-why-are-countries-freezing-their-funding/0000018d-550e-d0fc-a9bd-5f5f45020000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列校长在学校外遭枪击，受轻伤；警方逮捕四名嫌疑人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-principal-shot-wounded-outside-his-school-police-arrest-four-suspects/0000018d-59a8-d0fc-a9bd-5ffdcef60000</link><description>当局认为这起枪击事件与受害者大家庭之间的一场争斗有关。校长的兄弟 Hussam 去年 7 月被谋杀，享年 45 岁</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 11:02:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-principal-shot-wounded-outside-his-school-police-arrest-four-suspects/0000018d-59a8-d0fc-a9bd-5ffdcef60000</guid></item><item><title>在美国压力下，巴勒斯坦总理宣布全面振兴巴勒斯坦权力机构</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/following-u-s-pressure-palestinian-pm-declares-broad-revitalization-of-pa/0000018d-5987-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf5c750000</link><description>穆罕默德·什塔耶表示，新计划将分阶段实施，包括安全、经济和医疗保健方面的重大变化，但巴勒斯坦高级官员仍怀疑此举能否改善与以色列的关系</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 10:41:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/following-u-s-pressure-palestinian-pm-declares-broad-revitalization-of-pa/0000018d-5987-d0fc-a9bd-5fdf5c750000</guid></item><item><title>以色列支持拒绝释放亿万富翁罗曼·阿布拉莫维奇的捐赠资金</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-backs-refusal-to-release-billionaire-roman-abramovichs-funds-for-a-donation/0000018d-5601-d997-adff-df7be6320000</link><description>由于俄罗斯制裁，一家以色列银行拒绝从俄罗斯-以色列寡头的账户中转出220万美元，用于向以色列扎卡搜救组织捐款。总检察长表示她正在保护以色列银行免受风险</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israel-backs-refusal-to-release-billionaire-roman-abramovichs-funds-for-a-donation/0000018d-5601-d997-adff-df7be6320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队伪装成医生突袭约旦河西岸医院，打死三名哈马斯恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-bank-hospital-dressed-as-doctors-kill-three-hamas-terrorists/0000018d-5968-d997-adff-dd7aba630000</link><description>一支以色列卧底部队袭击了杰宁的伊本西纳医院，杀死了三名哈马斯附属人员。以色列安全部队表示，三人计划在不久的将来发动袭击</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 09:34:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-raid-west-bank-hospital-dressed-as-doctors-kill-three-hamas-terrorists/0000018d-5968-d997-adff-dd7aba630000</guid></item><item><title>尽管美国和卡塔尔持乐观态度，但以色列与哈马斯的协议仍然难以实现</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-american-and-qatari-optimism-israel-hamas-deal-remains-elusive/0000018d-56f0-d997-adff-dffa95590000</link><description>美国需要一项成就 — — 比如释放以色列人质 — — 但它已经对内塔尼亚胡的政策失去了耐心 ■ 伊朗尚未为其地区骚乱付出代价，华盛顿正在努力避免局势进一步升级 ■ 真主党正在准备与以色列国防军迫在眉睫的广泛冲突</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 04:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/despite-american-and-qatari-optimism-israel-hamas-deal-remains-elusive/0000018d-56f0-d997-adff-dffa95590000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队承认正在淹没加沙的哈马斯隧道以摧毁它们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-unrwa-to-act-on-highly-credible-allegations-against-staffers-in-gaza/0000018d-5876-d997-adff-dd7e7b5f0000</link><description>拜登称已就如何应对驻约旦美军袭击做出决定 ■ 哈马斯领导人伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚表示，哈马斯正在审查停火提案 ■ 三名通缉的哈马斯成员在以色列国防军袭击杰宁医院时被杀 ■ 布林肯敦促近东救济工程处按照“高度可信”采取行动针对加沙工作人员的指控 ■ 英国外长表示，英国考虑承认巴勒斯坦国 ■ 布林肯将于周六访问以色列 ■ 胡塞武装称他们已准备好与美国、英国进行“长期对抗” ■ 内塔尼亚胡：以色列不会释放数千名恐怖分子参与人质交易</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 03:49:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article-live/blinken-urges-unrwa-to-act-on-highly-credible-allegations-against-staffers-in-gaza/0000018d-5876-d997-adff-dd7e7b5f0000</guid></item><item><title>现在在加沙隧道内作战，以色列国防军知道杀死哈马斯领导人不会结束其统治</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-inside-gaza-tunnels-idf-knows-that-killing-hamas-leaders-wont-end-its-rule/0000018d-572b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7fa3850000</link><description>以色列高级军官相信，哈马斯地道内的战斗将提供有关该组织领导人及其仍扣押的以色列人质的宝贵情报</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 01:15:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/now-fighting-inside-gaza-tunnels-idf-knows-that-killing-hamas-leaders-wont-end-its-rule/0000018d-572b-d0fc-a9bd-5f7fa3850000</guid></item><item><title>总理办公室同意修复内塔尼亚胡私人住宅泳池后，以色列官员辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-to-quit-after-pms-bureau-okays-repairs-to-pool-at-netanyahus-home/0000018d-570b-d997-adff-df7becd90000</link><description>首席会计师与总理办公室其他官员发生冲突，最近一次是因为内塔尼亚胡位于凯撒利亚的庞大住宅的游泳池和住宅区的维修问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 00:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-official-to-quit-after-pms-bureau-okays-repairs-to-pool-at-netanyahus-home/0000018d-570b-d997-adff-df7becd90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战时内阁讨论哈马斯人质交易；消息人士称，大多数问题都已达成共识</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-discusses-hostage-deal-sources-uderstandings-emerge-on-most-issues/0000018d-56be-d0fc-a9bd-5eff2c950000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡办公室否认谈判取得进展的报道，但接受国土报采访的消息人士表示，核心问题是停火问题。周一早些时候，作为谈判的一部分，以色列代表团访问了埃及</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jan 2024 21:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-29/ty-article/.premium/israeli-war-cabinet-discusses-hostage-deal-sources-uderstandings-emerge-on-most-issues/0000018d-56be-d0fc-a9bd-5eff2c950000</guid></item></channel></rss>